# Branded .pptx/.potx templates go in this directory.
#
# They are git-ignored (see the repo .gitignore) because org templates are often
# proprietary. Symlink yours in, or commit only a neutral house template you own, then
# point the builder at it:
#
#     PRESO_TEMPLATE=templates/your-brand.pptx ./build.sh
#
# The builder works with no template at all (plain slides). This .gitkeep just keeps the
# directory present in a fresh clone.
